GSHPx is a selenium encompassing enzyme that provides protection against lipid peroxidation. It catalysis the breakdown of H 2O 2 and organic hydroperoxides (R-OOH) by glutathione (γGlu.Cys.Gly) as per following chemical reaction [ 50].
\documentclass[12pt]{minimal} \usepackage{amsmath} \usepackage{wasysym} \usepackage{amsfonts} \usepackage{amssymb} \usepackage{amsbsy} \usepackage{mathrsfs} \usepackage{upgreek} \setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt} \begin{document}$$ \mathrm{ROOH}+2\mathrm{GSH}\to \mathrm{ROH}+\mathrm{GSSG}+\mathrm{H}2\mathrm{O} $$\end{document}
ROOH + 2 GSH → ROH + GSSG + H 2 O
